Class DaoStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • OrmLiteSqliteOpenHelper
      • mil.nga.giat.mage.sdk.datastore.DaoStore

  • public class DaoStore
extends OrmLiteSqliteOpenHelper
    This is an implementation of OrmLite android database Helper. Go here to get daos that you may need. Manage your table creation and update strategies here as well.
